    <title>SciELO  Brasil - The Correlates of Brazil’s Military Expenditures, 1822-1945: The Politics of Defense Policy in a Non-Democratic Era The Correlates of Brazil’s Military Expenditures, 1822-1945: The Politics of Defense Policy in a Non-Democratic Era </title>

    
  
